summary.ar: أعكسي جمالك الساحر في المناسبات المختلفة باختيار هذا الفستان الأنيق، مصمم بقصة إيه لاين دون أكمام ليُضفي مزيدًا من الجاذبية عليك، مع نمط قوالب ملوّنة يعزز من مظهرك، مصنوع من خامة ناعمة ومساميّة تضمن لك الشعور التّام بالارتياح.
summary.en: Exhibiting a two-tone panelled design, this midi dress by Trendyol is sure to keep you ahead of style. It features a round neck, sleeveless pattern, A-line silhouette and single button closure across the back. Moreover, this day time-worthy dress is well-tailored from quality fabric to lend you a skin-friendly feel and breathable fit.

summary.en: For a casual event, keep your style sophisticated and chic with this mini dress by Vero Moda. The rich colour and all-over print give a visually appealing look to this piece. It features a collared neck, long sleeves, button-down closure and belted waist. Moreover, this dress is tailor-made from handpicked fabric to keep you at the utmost ease all the time.

By buying cotton products from Splash, you’re supporting more sustainable cotton farming through the Better Cotton Initiative (BCI). Better Cotton is sourced via mass balance.
